{"tid":1813163,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"It’s just a story!","createTime":"2020-01-06T05:20:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-27T10:08:52.000Z","uid":234961,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"8f3f184f134331bf29b675464f06b8d6a3d39b86","tid":1813163,"uid":234961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T05:20:22.000Z","msg":"某一年，政府經濟不景，失業率大增。國家外憂內患 : 外面有其他國家打擊，內部有權力危機。人心渙散，國家面臨覆滅。忽然某菜市場爆發新型病毒感染。三大河流同時迅速受污染。政府新聞若穩若現咁發放病毒感染消息，一方面控制評論，滅聲，另一方面又默許某啲消息廣傳一段時間，造成一段時間內人心惶惶，傳言四起。<br />\n<br />\n結果人民只能依賴某政黨，該政黨亦係病毒肆虐得差唔多之後成功研發疫苗。最後風平浪靜，病毒風波得以解決。人心歸邊，支持政黨。經濟問題，失業問題迎刃而解。<br />\n<br />\n我只係講緊套V煞姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />大家仲唔帶口罩？<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/9euW2xG01uY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F9euW2xG01uY&d=bwUHcV0Pscj1NrVo4Cy%2FDf7c%2B9HD3JYLAdxAiSxEDXo%3D&h=b0da675a\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/9euW2xG01uY</a><br />\n<br />\n買口罩攻略<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/n95market\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fn95market&d=bwUHcV0Pscj1NrVo4Cy%2FDf7c%2B9HD3JYLAdxAiSxEDXo%3D&h=eff8fe69\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/n95market</a>"},{"pid":"ecaee40074e0c21570f73f5f3bce768fe055337b","tid":1813163,"uid":234961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T05:22:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6fa724ef8a497ef14c82ddd9494504d1718e9f80","tid":1813163,"uid":234961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T05:22:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0f71da0bca0339e1850ba835ef6409eff6b4bd6c","tid":1813163,"uid":234961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T05:24:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a9141c1d94520e10a667a544ee46622f32b0372","tid":1813163,"uid":234961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T05:27:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkg